- ## 1 ## Steps TO Start React-Bootstrap
- # 1. Install it 
- npm install react-bootstrap bootstrap
- # 2. Import it
- add following at index.js or your layout
- import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
- import 'bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.js';
- # 3. Import from react-bootstrap
- which we use react bootstrap we import it from react-bootstrap like using { ctrl + space }
- import from on secound option react-bootstrap not from bootstrap show in options


- ## COMPONENTS ## --

- # 1. Alert (dismissible,Alert.Heading, Alert.Link, show(true, false))
- basically alert used like toaster to show alert on api success or any response like it have 7 types.
- always write variant name in small letter.
- dismissible property for add close as toaster (X) at top right at alert.
- if show set true the alert dismissible not work, not complasray use show.
- we can set dismissible by state
- 'primary','secondary','success','danger','warning','info','light','dark',
- <>  
           <Container>
                <Card>
                    <Alert show={true} variant="danger" dismissible>
                        <Alert.Heading>Heading</Alert.Heading>
                        <Alert.Link href="https://hypd.store/" target="_blank">This is Link</Alert.Link>
                        <p>this is alert paragraph</p>
                    </Alert>
                    <hr/>
                </Card>
            </Container>
</>
- Container is give you same space around left- right like one container.
- Card Show Card with Boarder

- # 2. Badges (bg, pill(give round shape))
- set badge on any like on any button, at shopping Cart product num. show
- <Button variant="primary">
       Profile <Badge pill bg="secondary">9</Badge>
  </Button>
- pill for round shape to badge

- # 3. Stack (direction , gap)
- used for show in direction set of item (stack) horizontal or vertical.
- <Stack direction="horizontal" gap={2}>
      <Badge bg="primary">Primary</Badge>
      <Badge bg="secondary">Secondary</Badge>
      <Badge bg="dark">Dark</Badge>
  </Stack>

- # 4 Accordion ()
- Click the accordions below to expand/collapse the accordion content.
- <Accordion defaultActiveKey="0">
    <Accordion.Item>
        <Accordion.Header> Item 1</Accordion.Header>
            <Accordion.Body>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur</p>
            </Accordion.Body>
        </Accordion.Item>
    </Accordion>

- # 5 Breadcrumbs
- Breadcrumbs is used for show navigation of web site.
- like i go home page then profile then Change Password
: home/profile/changepassword
- How use give in Program Folder file

- # 6 Button, Button-Group
- used to make button group Can made button group with dropdown button, input
- for use follow react-bootstrap official document.

- # 7 Card
- use react card
- Card, Card.Header, Card.Body, 

